sub_fields.instructions: Select Image Size

sub_fields.label: Image Object Fit
sub_fields.name: image_object_fit
sub_fields.instructions: Object-fit property is used to specify how image should be resized to fit its container (similar to background-size). Default val: "cover"

sub_fields.label: Image Object Position
sub_fields.name: image_object_position
sub_fields.instructions: The object-position property is used together with object-fit to specify how an image should be positioned with x/y coordinates inside its container.

sub_fields.name: footer_hook
sub_fields.instructions: Add custom code right before the closing </body> tag. Accepts any valid HTML including script and style tags.
